# Playwright visual snapshot baselines
# These ARE committed — they are the canonical regression baselines for
# `toHaveScreenshot()` assertions. Do NOT add `tests/e2e/*-snapshots/` back.
# (Playwright test run output — HTML reports, traces, screenshots from
# failure-only runs — lives in playwright-report/ and test-results/ which
# remain ignored.)
# tests/e2e/*-snapshots/
.wrangler/

# Decap CMS local cache
.decap/

# graphify skill output (chunked knowledge-graph artifacts)
/graphify-out/
/src/graphify-out/

# Stray Chrome profile files that were accidentally committed with
# absolute Windows-style paths. (Lighthouse creates these on Windows
# hosts when invoked via WSL.) Keep this rule so future `git add .`
# runs do not re-stage them.
undefined:*

# Harness session overlay (per-user SDD task reports + plan briefs).
# Lives next to the repo at <project>/.superpowers/ and is recreated
# by the Claude Code harness on each session — do not commit per-user
# session artifacts to the project repo. The plan files that drive
# the actual work live under docs/superpowers/ instead.
.superpowers/

# Hand-authored design doc — separate from the project. Author keeps it
# out of the repo.
DESIGN.md
